_:cb1420056ecab70121706c3d6a0ed49d2f0afba89e1882f0a9d38dc5bb0d4306cff <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#message> "cr:RegulatoryInteraction must carry cr:meetingType (Pre-IND, EOP1, EOP2, Type-A/B/C)." .
_:cb1420056ecab70121706c3d6a0ed49d2f0afba89e1882f0a9d38dc5bb0d4306cff <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#minCount> "1"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer> .
_:cb1420056ecab70121706c3d6a0ed49d2f0afba89e1882f0a9d38dc5bb0d4306cff <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#path> <https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#meetingType> .
